<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation states that action helpers are accessed using $this-&gt;_helpers property of the controller, while they are actually accessed using $this-&gt;_helper property, eg.:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
// INCORRECT
$flashMessenger = $this-&gt;_helpers-&gt;getHelper('FlashMessenger');
// CORRECT
$flashMessenger = $this-&gt;_helper-&gt;getHelper('FlashMessenger');
</code></pre>

<p>Please check 7.8 Action Helpers chapter.</p>

